# Falling Sky — Map Data 
# 
# Format: Region header, then indented tribe lines
# [CITY_NAME] = tribe has a city (gray diamond, caps on map)
# (rhenus) = adjacency crosses the Rhenus river (March halts, 1.3.5)
# (coastal) = adjacency is Britannia's sea connection (March/Scout restricted, 1.3.4)
# aedui-only / arverni-only / germanic-only = stacking restriction on that tribe circle

# 30 tribes total in base game (1.3.2)
# In Ariovistus: -Catuvellauni +Nori = still 30 (A1.3.2)


### BELGICA (3 regions, 7 tribes)

Morini | Belgica | CV 2 | adj: Nervii, Atrebates, Sugambri(rhenus), Catuvellauni(coastal)
  Menapii
  Morini

Nervii | Belgica | CV 2 | adj: Morini, Atrebates, Treveri, Sugambri(rhenus)
  Eburones
  Nervii

Atrebates | Belgica | CV 3 | adj: Morini, Nervii, Treveri, Carnutes, Mandubii, Catuvellauni(coastal), Veneti
  Bellovaci
  Atrebates
  Remi


### GERMANIA (2 regions, 4 tribes)
# Design note 7.2: CV = tribe count excluding Suebi

Sugambri | Germania | CV 1 | adj: Ubii, Morini(rhenus), Nervii(rhenus), Treveri(rhenus)
  Suebi (North) germanic-only
  Sugambri

Ubii | Germania | CV 1 | adj: Sugambri, Treveri(rhenus), Sequani(rhenus), Cisalpina 
  Suebi (South) germanic-only
  Ubii


### CELTICA (9 regions, 17 tribes)

Treveri | Celtica | CV 1 | adj: Nervii, Atrebates, Mandubii, Sequani, Sugambri(rhenus), Ubii(rhenus) 
  Treveri  

Carnutes | Celtica | CV 2 | adj: Atrebates, Mandubii, Pictones, Bituriges, Veneti
  Carnutes [CENABUM]
  Aulerci

Mandubii | Celtica | CV 3 | adj: Atrebates, Treveri, Carnutes, Aedui, Sequani, Bituriges
  Mandubii [ALESIA]
  Senones 
  Lingones

Veneti | Celtica | CV 2 | adj: Pictones, Catuvellauni(coastal), Carnutes
  Veneti
  Namnetes

Pictones | Celtica | CV 2 | adj: Veneti, Carnutes, Bituriges, Arverni
  Pictones
  Santones

Bituriges | Celtica | CV 1 | adj: Carnutes, Pictones, Aedui, Arverni, Mandubii
  Bituriges [AVARICUM]

Aedui | Celtica | CV 1 | adj: Mandubii, Bituriges, Sequani, Arverni, Helvii
  Aedui [BIBRACTE] aedui-only

Sequani | Celtica | CV 2 | adj: Treveri, Mandubii, Aedui, Arverni, Ubii(rhenus), Helvii, Cisalpina
  Sequani [VESONTIO]
  Helvetii

Arverni | Celtica | CV 3 | adj: Pictones, Bituriges, Aedui, Sequani, Helvii
  Arverni [GERGOVIA] arverni-only
  Cadurci
  Volcae


### BRITANNIA (1 region, 1 tribe)

Catuvellauni | Britannia | CV 1 | coastal-adj: Morini, Atrebates, Veneti
  Catuvellauni
  NOTE: in Ariovistus — not playable, Catuvellauni removed (A1.3.4)


### PROVINCIA (1 region, 1 tribe)

Helvii | Provincia | CV 1 | adj: Arverni, Sequani, Cisalpina, Aedui 
  Helvii 
  NOTE: permanent fort, supply line terminus, Roman home region


### CISALPINA (1 region, 0 tribes base / 1 tribe Ariovistus)

Cisalpina | Cisalpina | CV 0 | adj: Provincia, Sequani, Ubii
  NOTE: not playable unless Gallia Togata event (card 5) makes it a region
  NOTE: in Ariovistus — always playable, add Nori tribe (CV becomes 1), alps crossing rules (A3.2.2)
